{"tid":603828,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"業內專家出庭作證，C朗如不和解或面臨10年監禁","createTime":"2018-03-24T06:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T12:48:05.000Z","uid":20634,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9d55a82ca2c4db8ee4250feb9a563b18740a36","tid":603828,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"西班牙時間昨天中午，3名來自西班牙國際稅務司的業內專家在馬德里地方法院出庭作證，證實了西班牙稅務部門對C朗1470萬歐元稅務罪名的指控。<br />\n<br />\n據這3名業內專家稱，C朗的稅務問題是「前所未有的」，並且他們贊同西班牙稅務部門對C朗的指控，認為C朗應該為他的肖像權收入繳納稅款。<br />\n<br />\n據塞爾電台向法庭內部的消息源確認，當前擺在C朗面前的只有一種選擇：與檢方達成庭外和解。如果C朗拒絕談判和解，那麼他將會面臨至少4項罪名指控，總計不低於10年的監禁。"},{"pid":"e8ac3db7bc2847d4e7bcdf03c8ac9a26b3a4b0fa","tid":603828,"uid":19126,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"監獄杯有a johnson 對丙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83566cbdcc86b57fb776114003ff283a22eb90a","tid":603828,"uid":20634,"like":231,"dislike":4,"score":227,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T06:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/141924_556b9c036c4a95275ff6b6d947c32283.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F141924_556b9c036c4a95275ff6b6d947c32283.png&h=aba1e293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb2d91a72fa2491c8b188e1feda39daa28f151d","tid":603828,"uid":35176,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"拳擊有泰臣 籃球有高比 足球有我朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67d75d4dffd8961b0296d8064fe99d65ca0a706","tid":603828,"uid":12628,"like":23,"dislike":18,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"快啲拉左呢條垃圾，比愛滋基佬插爆屎眼啦"},{"pid":"3f988715bfb38edcc1f95f12dabc7614d26c22dc","tid":603828,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0